*nix Install Instructions:
--------------------------

$ git clone https://mdwhatcott@github.com/mdwhatcott/VimConfig.git ~/.vim
$ cd ~/.vim
$ chmod +x install.sh
$ ./install.sh


Windows Install Instructions:
-----------------------------
C:\> git clone https://mdwhatcott@github.com/mdwhatcott/VimConfig.git  %HOME%\vimfiles
C:\> cd %HOME%\vimfiles
C:\> git submodule update --init
C:\> cd ..
C:\> mklink %HOME%\.vimrc %HOME%\vimfiles\vimrc
C:\> mklink %HOME%\.gvimrc %HOME%\vimfiles\gvimrc


Adding pathogen style plugins:
------------------------------
$ cd ~/.vim
$ git submodule add <url-to-repository> bundle/<name-of-plugin>
$ git add -A
$ git commit -m "Added <name-of-plugin>"
$ git push origin master
